block docs-content
  div
    p Cards are simple way to present data in a boxed container. Default Cards does not apply any style to the cards and you are free to use utility classes to create cards of different styles.

    h2 Cards With Border
    p Use the <code>.border</code> or <code>.border-dark</code> utility classes to apply border to the card.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        .grid.gutters.mt-4
          .col
            .p.border.border-soft
              .h3 Card Title
              .text-muted Card subtitle
              p A simple card with border and soft edges.
              a.button.button-purple Buy Now
          .col
            .border.border-soft
              .p.bg-light
                .h4.font-medium Card Header
              .p
                div A common card design with header and footer.<br>Another line.
              .p.border-top
                a.button.button-green.mt-0.mr-1 Accept
                a.button.mt-0 Cancel
