    h2 Cards With Shadow
    p Use the <code>.shadow</code>, <code>.shadow-md</code> and <code>.shadow-hover</code> utility classes to apply shadow to the card.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        .grid.gutters.mt-4
          .col
            .p.border-soft.shadow
              .h3 Card Title
              .text-muted Card subtitle
              p Card with shadow and soft edges.
              a.button.button-red Buy Now
          .col
            .p.border-soft.shadow-md.shadow-hover
              .h3 Card Title
              .text-muted Card subtitle
              p Card with shadow-md and shadow hover.
              a.button.button-red Buy Now
