    h2 Cards With Background Color
    p Use color utility classes to specify background color of the card.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        .grid.gutters.mt-4
          .col

            .p-4.border-rounded.bg-gray-light
              .h3 Card Title
              .text-muted Card subtitle
              p Card with gray light background.
              a.button.button-green Buy Now
          .col

            .p-4.border-rounded.bg-dark.text-white
              .h3 Card Title
              .text-gray Card subtitle
              p Card with dark background.
              a.button.button-purple Buy Now
